This behaviour is also reproducible with the following test:
```js
test(`${upMethod} - input-validation data stream`, t => {
  t.plan(2)
  sget({
    method: upMethod,
    url: 'http://localhost:' + fastify.server.address().port + '/',
    body: fs.createReadStream(path.join(__dirname, '/input-validation.js'))
  }, (err, response, body) => {
    t.error(err)
    t.strictEqual(response.statusCode, 200)
  })
})
```

